          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Criminal Alien Removal Clarification Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to subject to deportation an alien who at any time after admission has been convicted of a felony or two misdemeanors under state or federal law.</p> </p>]]></text>
